cast.overview: Upstanding community leader Nils has just won an award for "Citizen of the Year" when he learns the news that his son has died of a heroin overdose. Suspecting foul play, Nils begins to investigate, and soon finds himself at the center of an escalating underworld gang war between Serbian drug dealers and a sociopathic criminal mastermind known only as “The Count.”
cast.title: In Order of Disappearance

details.biography:
Sergej Trifunović ( born 2 September 1972 in Mostar, SR Bosnia and Herzegovina, SFR Yugoslavia) is a popular Serbian movie actor.
